title: The Cozmic Cafe and Pub
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. At the historic Pearson's Soda Works Building in downtown, its menu includes many ovo-lacto vegetarian dishes (salads, veggie burgers, scrambles). Vegans can ask to omit cheese. Hosts open mic night, live music, and other events. Bar with a food menu is open for late night events.
